article.headline: San Diego St. 65, Air Force 34
article.story: SAN DIEGO -- Billy White scored 15 points and Richie Williams added 12 points and five assists to lift San Diego State to a 65-34 win over Air Force Academy Saturday night. It was the fourth consecutive win for the Aztecs, 17-5, who are tied atop the Mountain West Conference with Utah at 7-2. Air Force, which is 9-13 overall and 0-9 in the conference, has lost 10 straight games. The Aztecs led 33-14 at the half and led by as many as 33 points.
